{
  "stem": "22889.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, right in my bottom-- lower-back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I was surprised Mark was in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, only a short time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he was-- you know he was in Krakow?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could have sent him to Mielec, maybe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he left Krakow before they went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Is that right?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Goerlitz?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Poecking, that other camp was Poecking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I said, from the beginning, we arrived 400 men, April the 1st.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were liberated May the 2nd.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Three days before liberation-- before our liberation, we seen they were setting explosives around the camp, because the American forces, they were approaching.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they were going to blow up the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't want-- they didn't want to leave any traces.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, there were four of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very close friends with each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We decided we're going to escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were going to be killed, anyhow, so what do we have to do is we take a chance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So about three days before liberation, we escape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were no electric fences, wires, just the regular wires, barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at night, we get out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In this-- in that camp, the guards, they were Hungarians, Hungarian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They fought with the Germans on the German side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't forget.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were guarding us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't care so much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we escaped, four of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My friend lives in Antwerp, Belgium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One lives in New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think he passed away, already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And his brother, which he lives in-- in Tel Aviv, on Herzliya Street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was, before the war, Adam Naparstek.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Today, his name is Adam Naor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Naor, in Hebrew, means naparstek.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Naparstek, it's a-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
